Guvf vf Gnfx 13 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Jrera'g gubfr yvfgf sha gb cynl jvgu?  Lbh fubhyq trg hfrq gb gurz, gurl
ner hfrq nyy bire gur xreary va ybgf bs qvssrerag cynprf.

Abj gung jr ner nyybpngvat n fgehpgher gung jr jnag gb hfr n ybg bs, jr
zvtug jnag gb fgneg pnevat nobhg gur fcrrq bs gur nyybpngvba, naq abg
unir gb jbeel nobhg gur perngvba bs gubfr bowrpgf sebz gur "trareny"
zrzbel cbbyf bs gur xreary.

Guvf gnfx vf gb gnxr gur pbqr jevggra va gnfx 12, naq pnhfr nyy zrzbel
nyybpngrq sebz gur 'fgehpg vqragvgl' gb pbzr sebz n cevingr fyno pnpur
whfg sbe gur sha bs vg.

Vafgrnq bs hfvat xznyybp() naq xserr() va gur zbqhyr, hfr
xzrz_pnpur_nyybp() naq xzrz_pnpur_serr() vafgrnq.  Bs pbhefr guvf zrnaf
lbh jvyy unir gb vavgvnyvmr lbhe zrzbel pnpur cebcreyl jura gur zbqhyr
fgnegf hc.  Qba'g sbetrg gb qb gung.  Lbh ner serr gb anzr lbhe zrzbel
pnpur jungrire lbh jvfu, ohg vg fubhyq fubj hc va gur /cebp/fynovasb
svyr.

Qba'g fraq gur shyy zbqhyr sbe guvf gnfx, bayl n cngpu jvgu gur qvss
sebz gnfx 12 fubjvat gur yvarf punatrq.  Guvf zrnaf lbh jvyy unir gb
xrrc n pbcl bs lbhe 12 gnfx erfhygf fbzrjurer gb znxr fher lbh qba'g
birejevgr gurz.

Nyfb fubj gur bhgchg bs /cebp/fynovasb jvgu lbhe zbqhyr ybnqrq.
